Romy and Michele's High School Reunion;;1997;;R;;Comedy;;6.3;;David Mirkin;;Mira Sorvino,Lisa Kudrow,Janeane Garofalo,Alan Cumming,Julia Campbell,Mia Cottet,Kristin Bauer van Straten,Elaine Hendrix,Vincent Ventresca,Camryn Manheim,Justin Theroux,Jacob Vargas,Tami-Adrian George,Neil Dickson,E.J. Callahan,Kathy Long,Betsy Folsom,Zack Phifer;;Romy and Michele have been through it all, including being tortured by the Popular crowd when in high school. When they receive word of a 10 year reunion, they come to realize their lives aren't as impressive as they'd like them to be. Instead of staying home they go to the reunion with business outfits, cell phones, and one heck of a bogus success story.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0120032/